Description of incident: Flewelling & Mitton PC notified individuals of a data breach when their offices were broken into the morning of December 11, 2015. The individual broke the locks on several file cabinets that contained customer information.The information compromised included names and Social Security numbers. They stated that the only thing stolen was petty cash.More Information: https://www.oag.state.md.us/idtheft/Breach%20Notices/2015/itu-262309.pdf
